title: U.S. Law-Enforcement Agencies Seek to Combat AI Bias
description: The Justice Department and other agencies are focused on how ChatGPT and other AI tools could be used to discriminate or harm competition.

title: Microsoft Earnings Growth Likely Slowed Last Quarter Amid Economic Concerns
description: The software giant’s cloud computing business has decelerated as companies become more cautious.

title: TikTok, Twitter, Meta Face Countdown to Comply With Tough Content Law
description: The world’s most far-reaching digital-content law will oblige 19 social-media, search and e-commerce services to comply with strict new rules by late August.

title: Google Ad Revenue Expected to Drop for Second Straight Quarter
description: Search giant is trying to jump-start growth amid a volatile digital ad market and competition in AI.
